# Group Authentication

## Auth [/auth]

### Authenticate [POST]

+ Request (application/json;charset=UTF-8)

        {
            "username": "admin",
            "password": "admin"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "_links": {"self": {"href": "http://superdesk.apiary.io/auth/523"}},
            "token": "aNcdefgH",
            "user": "123"
        }

The rest of the endpoints requiring authorization will have to supply the following header:
"Authorization": b'basic ' + b64encode(token + b':')

